Membership
Deer Island is surrounded by water.
At Deer Island Country Club you’ll be surrounded by friends!
Isn’t it time you join “the island!”
From the moment you pass onto the gated causeway to Deer Island, you’ll be taken by the sheer natural beauty of our Florida wetlands setting.
Then, right in the middle of it all, you’ll find Deer Island Country Club — one of the finest tracks for challenging-yet-enjoyable golf in all of Florida.
If you’re taken by the beauty and by the course – why not join us!
Deer Island CC offers both single and family annual memberships.
Benefits include:
Preferred tee times
Unlimited use of the driving range and practice area
Swimming pool privileges
Discounts on golf shop merchandise
This is a great place to “show off” for friends, family, business associates – and yourself!
Just imagine sealing a business deal out on the course, among the flora and fauna.
For every reason to join a country club – the answer is Deer Island CC!
Get the membership best suited for you, be it single or family; resident or non.
Enjoy the feeling of seclusion playing our island course. You’ll feel special every time you cross that gated causeway to Deer Island CC.
Enjoy “Old-Florida” hospitality with family and friends in our Old Florida-style clubhouse. And be assured that that family feeling comes through in all of our employees as well.
For Inquiries:
Contact our Pro Shop at (352) 343-7550

Full memberships for families and individual memberships are available for each membership category.
Membership is subject to Membership Committee acceptance. Prices are subject to change at any time without notice and applicable sales tax applies.
